{
  "stem": "20021.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We turned around and went.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And this was started like, at 6:00, 7:00 o'clock at night.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We reached that house from his description.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It must have been the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We knocked on the door.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "The guy came out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Yes, I'm waiting for you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[SOB] The next day, he took us in his truck and took us to Arad, which was a large town, relatively large town-- many Jews, a Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And they were free at that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "They were-- you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I stayed in Arad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I must have-- this must have been already June, say, because I left in May.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It must have been June.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I stayed in Arad for a whole month.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And because I remember I had a girlfriend, with whom I spoke Hebrew, you see?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I used-- I knew fluent Hebrew from my school years in Tarnow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she learned Hebrew, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She, altogether, she spoke Hebrew, she spoke French, and she spoke English, and she spoke German, fluent all the four languages, fluent-- very intelligent girl.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you know, we were friends and all that, and stayed in Arad.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the idea was that we can not stay Arad forever because it's too little a town and all that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And arrangements were being made to help us get to Bucharest.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they did make those arrangement, and we got to Bucharest.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the Jewish community-- in Arad, there was already-- already a little bureaucracy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a president in the Jewish community and all that, and I don't know exactly their arrangements.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we were taken care of.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were treated as, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we came to Bucharest, and somebody else took us over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was a house.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
